data.description: This home has an assumable mortgage at 2.75% interest. All the character of historic West Seventh with an open floor plan and fantastic light. Hardwood floors, original mouldings, 10' ceilings. A quality kitchen designed for serious cooking and entertaining. Professional grade appliances featuring Cafe-Series dual in-wall ovens. Gracious, well-lit dining and living room spaces. Neat, clean basement with room for storage/finishing. New central air, newer water heater. Walk-up attic space with even more future promise. Oversized garage and decent neighbors. Quiet, secluded nook of West Seventh!
